Scenario 1: Cover Letter from upload or pasted text
- Select document type = cover letter (CV)
- Paste url of targeted job and input other data fields
- Source select: User selects from local file dialog, extracting text into document field.
- Show results (realtime live)
- Drag and drop (insert) the data fields into the document text locations
- Edit document text
- User approves current version (Saves session)
- User downloads generated file locally


Scenario 2: AI Assisted Cover Letter
- Select document type = cover letter (CV)
- Paste url of targeted job and input other data fields
- Source select: AI 
- AI prompts user for context, tone and positional interest. Generates initial document
- Show results (realtime live)...

Pseudo -----------------------------------------
Mclean Pseudo: Linear

Welcome screen
Prompt for document type
Initialize document class
Show main screen with data fields in right column
